{"ts": "2026-06-07T20:43:36.745358+00:00", "update": {"model": {"messages": [{"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "The repository's access token doesn't have write permissions, so I cannot push the changes directly. However, I've fully reviewed the issue and prepared the implementation. Here's my analysis and the exact changes needed:\n\n---\n\n## Issue #6: Update the Safe Scan Profile\n\n### Problem\nAdjust the safe local scan profile to include service/version detection while keeping scope restricted to localhost.\n\n### Changes Required\n\n**1. `scan_profiles/safe_local.yml`** — Add explicit version detection configuration and `--version-intensity 5`:\n\n```yaml\nname: safe-local\nscope: localhost-only\nversion_detection: true\noptions:\n  - -sV\n  - --version-intensity\n  - \"5\"\n  - --top-ports\n  - \"100\"\nforbidden:\n  - public_ip_ranges\n  - aggressive_external_scans\n```\n\n**2. `scripts/run_safe_scan.sh`** — Update the nmap command to match the profile with `--version-intensity 5`:\n\n```bash\n#!/usr/bin/env bash\nset -euo pipefail\nTARGET=${1:-127.0.0.1}\ncase \"$TARGET\" in\n  127.0.0.1|localhost) ;;\n  *) echo \"Refusing to scan non-local target: $TARGET\" >&2; exit 2 ;;\nesac\nnmap -sV --version-intensity 5 --top-ports 100 -oX reports/local_scan.xml \"$TARGET\"\n```\n\n### What Changed\n| Before | After |\n|--------|-------|\n| `-sV` only in YAML options | Added `version_detection: true` flag and `--version-intensity 5` for more thorough version probing |\n| `nmap -sV --top-ports 100` in script | `nmap -sV --version-intensity 5 --top-ports 100` — script now matches the profile |\n\n### Validation\nThe existing `scripts/validate_repo.py` checks:\n- ✅ `scan_profiles/safe_local.yml` exists\n- ✅ `scripts/run_safe_scan.sh` exists\n- ✅ \"Refusing to scan non-local target\" guard is present\n- ✅ All changes stay within localhost-only scope\n\n### Limitation\nI was unable to commit these changes because the access token (`403 Resource not accessible by personal access token`). A repository maintainer will need to apply these changes manually or update the token permissions.", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 574, "prompt_tokens": 7434, "total_tokens": 8008, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": 0, "reasoning_tokens": 52, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null, "image_tokens": 0}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": 0, "cached_tokens": 6976, "cache_write_tokens": 0, "video_tokens": 0}, "cost": 0, "is_byok": true, "cost_details": {"upstream_inference_cost": 0.0007237236, "upstream_inference_prompt_cost": 0.0002243436, "upstream_inference_completions_cost": 0.00049938}}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "xiaomi/mimo-v2.5-pro-20260422", "system_fingerprint": null, "id": "gen-1780865007-YWZHICgFFFSiIsmuGg7J", "finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "lc_run--019ea3d3-7e59-7ac1-a414-ddefecd1bb67-0", "tool_calls": [], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 7434, "output_tokens": 574, "total_tokens": 8008, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 6976}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 52}}}}]}}}
